Dear [Employee Name],

We're thrilled to be assisting you with your relocation to [City name]!  We're excited to get started and make this transition as smooth as possible for you.

To help us understand your needs better and begin the process, we've scheduled a brief introductory phone call with one of our relocation specialists.  During this call, we'll discuss your preferences, timeline, and any specific requirements you may have.  This will help us tailor our services to perfectly match your needs.

We look forward to speaking with you soon!

Sincerely,
The [Relocation Company Name] Team
